      "writtenOn": "2016-04-07T21:35:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "multimap has the same interface, it just returns the first value for a key. I think having a more general interface would be useful here, it could even be a convenient way to find items in a string or a vector (with a specialization for containers that don\u0027t have a find method), perhaps with additional functions like findSequence and containsSequence.\n\nI don\u0027t feel very strongly about this though so if others are fine with this I won\u0027t push for it.",
      "parentUuid": "8ea2ccbd_48fd6850",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 30,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 40,
        "endChar": 73
      },
